thread.title: BRIEF-Northeast Pharmaceutical Group sees FY 2017 net profit up 360 pct to 400 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Northeast Pharmaceutical Group sees FY 2017 net profit up 360 pct to 400 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - northeast pharmaceutical group co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Northeast Pharmaceutical Group Co Ltd
* Says it sees net profit for FY 2017 to increase by 360 percent to 400 percent, or to be 110 million yuan to 120 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 23.8 million yuan
* Comments that increased vitamin C price as main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/V1o1yT
